00:12:30.440 --> 00:12:31.320
So, these days,

00:12:31.320 --> 00:12:32.360
I came every day for you.

00:12:33.750 --> 00:12:34.590
For me?

00:12:35.870 --> 00:12:36.750
Why?

00:12:38.670 --> 00:12:40.670
