00:13:05.750 --> 00:13:06.590
Mr. Song.

00:13:08.720 --> 00:13:10.230
Do you really often visit
the Fragrance House?

00:13:10.320 --> 00:13:11.160
I...

00:13:12.120 --> 00:13:12.960
I...

00:13:14.390 --> 00:13:15.870
