00:13:56.240 --> 00:13:57.120
I'm a lady

00:13:57.120 --> 00:13:58.480
who is spoiled and unruly.

00:14:00.150 --> 00:14:00.990
But that day,

00:14:01.320 --> 00:14:02.320
