00:14:24.870 --> 00:14:25.710
Then tell me.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:27.960
What's good about me?

00:14:36.600 --> 00:14:37.440
You...

00:14:41.200 --> 00:14:42.080
You are...

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:44.960
Well, you...

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:46.960
I understand.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:48.840
