00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:07.390
So, you're brave.

00:15:08.030 --> 00:15:09.910
A clever, brave,

00:15:10.240 --> 00:15:11.720
and pretty woman like you

00:15:11.960 --> 00:15:12.800
